          "settings": {
            "text_above": "In Sept 2025, while she was away at college, a dental office took a full mouth series of radiographs. The dentist diagnosed 12 cavities. \nThe patients wanted to try remineralization therapy first and began to use Dr. Jen's Super Paste twice a day. ",
