      "name": "C - Case Study",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Case Study",
        "text_1": "After 9 years of orthodontics, this patient had multiple interproximal lesions despite good homecare, Prevident 5000, a low pH diet, and flossing daily.",
        "text_2": "She continued to use the Prevident 5000, began MI Paste, and had regular applications of silver diamine fluoride. The lesions remained stable for 5 years. However, when she went off to college, all these protective measures diminished and the carries progressed.",
